Purpose: Manage question activation lifecycle and votes

Actions:
- activate({ question }) -> { activation } | { error }
- deactivate({ activation }) -> { activation } | { error }
- showResults({ activation }) -> { activation } | { error }
- hideResults({ activation }) -> { activation } | { error }
- vote({ activation, user, option }) -> { activation } | { error }

Queries:
- _getActivation({ activation }) -> [{ activation, question, isActive, showResults }]
- _getActiveByQuestion({ question }) -> [{ activation, isActive, showResults }]
- _getVotesByActivation({ activation }) -> [{ activation, user, option }]
- _getVoteCounts({ activation }) -> [{ option, count, total }]
- _getUserVote({ activation, user }) -> [{ option }]

State (MongoDB):
- activations: { activation, question, isActive, showResults }
- votes: { activation, user, option }

